<2ND_LINE>PM-Jackson, 1st Ld-Writethru, a0516,440</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>Jackson: N.H. Showing `Proved We Could Broaden Our Base'</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: Top 7 grafs new to update with morning quotes; Picks up 6th
