<2ND_LINE>AM-Digest Briefs,1185</2ND_LINE>
<NOTE>Eds: This package does not contain the following items from the
News Digest: BEIRUT, Lebanon _ Lebanon-Kidnap; UNDATED _ Political
Rdp; CONCORD, N.H. _ The South and Beyond; HEBRON, Occupied West
